1
03:05:26,561 --> 03:05:27,896
What was that?

2
03:05:28,689 --> 03:05:29,355
What happened?

3
03:05:29,607 --> 03:05:31,065
It fell. I saw it.

4
03:05:34,612 --> 03:05:35,612
It's dead.

5
03:05:39,867 --> 03:05:41,200
Smaug is dead.

6
03:05:42,078 --> 03:05:43,369
By my beard...

7
03:05:43,621 --> 03:05:45,412
...I think he's right.

8
03:05:45,665 --> 03:05:47,040
Look there!

9
03:05:49,001 --> 03:05:52,712
The Ravens of Erebor
are returning to the Mountain.

10
03:05:53,881 --> 03:05:54,546
Aye.

11
03:05:54,799 --> 03:05:56,257
Word will spread.

12
03:05:56,508 --> 03:05:57,508
Before long...

13
03:05:57,635 --> 03:06:00,428
...every soul in Middle-earth will know...

14
03:06:00,680 --> 03:06:02,763
...the dragon is dead!

